Document: SpinBox
Path: godot/classes/class_spinbox.rst
Summary: This section describes the properties available for the SpinBox control node.

*   alignment (HorizontalAlignment): Text alignment for the SpinBox's LineEdit. Default: 0
*   custom_arrow_round (bool): If true, the SpinBox's value will be rounded to the nearest integer when using the arrow buttons. Default: false
*   custom_arrow_step (float): The step value to use when incrementing or decrementing the SpinBox's value with the arrow buttons. Default: 0.0
*   editable (bool): If true, the SpinBox's LineEdit is editable. Default: true
*   prefix (String): A prefix string displayed before the value. Default: ""
*   select_all_on_focus (bool): If true, the text in the LineEdit will be selected when it gains focus. Default: false
*   size_flags_vertical (bitfield[SizeFlags]): Vertical size flags for the control. Default: 1 (overrides Control.size_flags_vertical)
*   step (float): The step value for incrementing or decrementing the SpinBox's value. Default: 1.0 (overrides Range.step)
*   suffix (String): A suffix string displayed after the value. Default: ""
*   update_on_text_changed (bool): If true, the SpinBox's value will update immediately as text is typed into the LineEdit. If false, the value only updates when the LineEdit loses focus or Enter is pressed. Default: false
